ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4c90b970b4430d3b2b4ea83e6621f546b355d","tid":1612582,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"44ebb83e0194252b67c8ce4a98506e981632da05","tid":1612582,"uid":313710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85583c4d0c45643f9538fce3018f2c2576284053","tid":1612582,"uid":78235,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"美帝真係好撚霸道， 好賤格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意"},{"pid":"4b20b4b2c1aba4a6ddce32fac66cb9a775f9ead6","tid":1612582,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d7759fd2c8cd27436f555046d27f4d693176d87a","tid":1612582,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"差役開槍之後，市面平靜至今。開槍的道理就在這裡。<br />\n很憤怒？對不起，在開槍之前你沒做對事情，你就要承擔開槍之後的事情。六四就是這樣開槍的，至今平反了沒有？繼續悼念六四吧，去太子站上香吧。<br />\n共產黨講的犯了政治錯誤，後果很嚴重。現在香港人犯的就是政治錯誤，不是打或不打的問題，是政治錯誤已經犯下了，還一直犯下去，一百幾十萬人這樣犯下去。還有得救嗎？<br />\n只有一群犯下政治錯誤的愚民，才會容許槍桿子裡面出政權這種事發生。但現在發生了在香港。<br />\n犯下政治錯誤的人民，沒資格讓子彈飛，沒資格玩拖延戰術、流水鬥爭，因為最終子彈會飛入他們的身體。"},{"pid":"718873974c6f84c519a661e5866eb08c562969aa","tid":1612582,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n係時候集中返係實際行動上 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\